# Studio Intelligence Data Dictionary

---

# Purpose

This document defines every metric, dimension, and warehouse table used by Studio Intelligence.

Each metric should exist only once within the warehouse and have one authoritative source system.

This document serves as the reference for:

- ETL development
- Dashboard development
- API development
- AI prompts
- Reporting
- Data governance

---

# Source Systems

| System | Purpose |
|---------|---------|
| Google Analytics 4 | Website analytics and attribution |
| Eulerity | Paid marketing performance |
| SOCi | Local marketing and social campaigns |
| PTS | Reservations, operations, and revenue |
| Supabase | Historical warehouse |

