# Metric Naming Standards

Use lowercase.

Use underscores.

Examples

```
total_users

new_users

average_session_duration

private_parties

gift_card_sales
```

Never use spaces.

Never abbreviate unless industry standard.

---

# Warehouse Standards

Every warehouse table should contain:

- studio_id
- studio_code
- studio_name
- date
- integration_type

Every ETL should:

- Normalize data
- UPSERT records
- Preserve history

